-All these guys are dead.

192
00:14:35,890 --> 00:14:37,760
Except you, of course.

193
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:44,020
And Doug Thompson, but l wish he were.
He let me eat a whole roll of Bolls Laxatives.

194
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:48,120
