-Don is important.
-You know, l found that guy

203
00:15:18,810 --> 00:15:21,770
working in a fur company, night school.

204
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:25,060
And that girl, Betty.

205
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:29,740
